quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,Watee jigok-gok bumoe le geumpa Nyan geumpa raya hanaban peugah
  99,2,Asoe lam bumoe jipeuteubiet le Geuhon bukon le bandum jiruah
  99,3,Watee nyan insan jikheun peue nyoe ka
  99,4,Bumoe kheun sigra teuma jipeugah
  99,5,Atra nyoe bandum wahi bak Tuhan Po gata Neukheun dum Neuyue ruah
  99,6,Uroe nyan teubiet dum manusia Meulaksin laksa le han ek peugah Meubagoe macam taeu uroe nyan Amai jih sinan dum geupeuleumah
  99,7,Barangsoe pubuet ube dhoi nyang got Jikalon meuhat teuma geubalah
  99,8,Barangsoe pubuet ube dhoi jeuheut Jikalon meuhat teuma geubalah